            <div type="translation">
                <p>if destined end brough even you under earth’s bosom, honorable late Sopatrus, be
                    well (=farewell) also amidst the dead. </p></div>
            
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Elegiac couplet. The left half of the inscription is missing and was seemingly
                    cut in modern times. The Atlas of Di Cesnola provides the Greek inscription in
                    full.</p></div>
            
